sentences: Caroline Thérese af Ugglas Liljedahl (born 7 April 1972) is a Swedish singer, artist and chorister.
Melodifestivalen 2007 with the song "Tror på dig", written by herself along with Heinz Liljedahl and Mattias Torell.
On 24 February 2007 she performed "Tro på dig", ending up in 6th place, which didn't qualify her any further in the contest.
Melodifestivalen 2009 with the track 'Snälla Snälla' (Please Please).
Melodifestivalen 2013 with the song "Hon har inte".
